during that meeting

00:01:26.780 --> 00:01:29.790 align:middle line:84%
and what it meant to us, what
we had the opportunity to share

00:01:29.790 --> 00:01:30.790 align:middle line:90%
with the United Nations.

00:01:30.790 --> 00:01:33.442 align:middle line:84%
So Bruce Lipton, thank
you so much for being

00:01:33.442 --> 00:01:35.900 align:middle line:84%
with us on "Missing Links" and
welcome to the show tonight.

00:01:35.900 --> 00:01:36.920 align:middle line:84%
